title: Mariah Carey (Part 2)
itunes:title: Mariah Carey (Part 2)
description:
It's Mariah week here on Questlove Supreme! On the heels of her courageously honest and compelling memoir, The Meaning of Mariah Carey, Mariah joins Quest and Team Supreme for a good no holds barred 2 part conversation. Check out part two where she gets real about her first marriage, independence and living this racially ambiguous life as a Black woman. Also, Mariah gives Team Supreme an exclusive listen to the 90's alt rock album she recorded under the moniker Chick.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
